                        <ul>
                            <li>Online fee collection on time</li>
                            <li>Communication to parents using mobile notifications, SMS and email</li>
                            <li>School bus GPS tracking</li>
                            <li>Online availability of progress report, marks list, timesheet</li>
                            <li>Attendance management of students by automating  it</li>
                            <li>Generating attendance reports of the students</li>
                            <li>Staff management using biometric system</li>
                            <li>Staff allocation to specific class and period</li>
                            <li>Generating financial report and administrative reports</li>
                            <li>No more manual records or calculations on sheets of paper.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div><!-- .row end-->
        </div><!-- .white_cnts end-->
    </div> <!-- .container end-->
</section> <!-- .whitebg end-->

